Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:05.50,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷いなく輝き続ける太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:07.24,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:10.15,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空の青を食いぬいたような雲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:11.44,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:14.46,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝寝坊を自由自在な毎日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:15.92,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ついに来た
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:17.77,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ついに来た
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:19.59,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ついに来た
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:20.78,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ついに来た
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:23.27,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ついに来たんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:28.22,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏休み
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:34.71,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おーい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.59,0:00:41.29,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あつ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:22.06,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊-ぼ-う-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:23.32,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:24.62,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ええ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:25.68,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なぜなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:29.24,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺には今救わねばならない人々が大勢いるからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:31.86,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人助け　何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:33.86,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐希まさかボランティアーとか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:34.78,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まあね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:39.45,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大金で動く男じゃありませんからね　俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:42.48,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おー　何　事件？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:46.17,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐希　早くしないと皆死んじゃうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:48.26,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そいつは大変だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.85,0:02:54.84,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴なんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:56.38,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:02:59.32,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帰れ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:01.97,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まだ何も言ってないんじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:04.03,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞かれなくてもわかったんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.82,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だったら話は早い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:06.67,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうする
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:07.38,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこ行く
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:08.76,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ね　どこ行く
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:11.49,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから遊びなんか行かねえっつの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:15.18,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺今課題やってるの  じゃあな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:16.65,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待ってください
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:18.55,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一分　一分でいいので
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:20.28,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話だけでも　話だけならいいじゃありませんか　奥さん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.49,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これ使えば　お肌つるつる　これ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:23.84,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お前が営業なんか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:27.85,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:30.31,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あれ　千鶴君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:32.94,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,よく家が分かりましたね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:34.16,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今暇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:35.37,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊び行かない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:39.77,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう…ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:42.01,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春ちゃんまでダメか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:43.98,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いいえ　そうじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:46.18,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうですね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:49.24,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,じゃあ　一緒にやりましょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:50.67,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一緒に？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:53.34,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.72,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お菓子作ってたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:58.09,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほとんどやったことなかったんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:00.97,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休みだし  やってみようかなあって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:02.48,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一緒にやりません
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.13,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まあいいか　やろうやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:08.29,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:11.24,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,じゃ　そこの生地混ぜてもらえますか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:12.20,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:13.05,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:17.36,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴君上手ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:22.11,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,またまたそんな　僕なんてまだまだですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:24.40,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いい匂い
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:26.73,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.65,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おいしくできるといいんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:31.75,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こんなものかな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:34.44,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春ちゃんばっか狡い
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:37.58,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　ごめんなさい　はい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:44.06,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わー　甘くてふわって口の中で広がって おいしいです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:46.89,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来上がり楽しみですね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:48.71,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうですね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:52.80,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,じゃあ　出来上がったらこれ皆のところにも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:54.60,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:57.42,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:58.57,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今の異空間は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:01.03,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺が俺でなくなんって気が
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:02.02,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あのう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:04.73,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飽きちゃいました
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:08.36,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でもここまで来たから 最後まで作らないと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:11.60,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作る？　新しい俺を
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:12.63,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:17.53,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこか遊び来たくて皆の家を回ってたんですね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:18.75,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.94,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,せっかくの夏休みなのにさ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:24.25,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆って涼しい部屋に籠っちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:27.06,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日特に暑いですからね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.37,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でも１カ月もあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:31.44,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと外で遊ぶことも
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:33.75,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ　じゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:35.39,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お祭りなんかどうですか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:36.38,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お祭り
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:37.93,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日あるんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:40.03,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜なら結構涼しいし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:42.54,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誘えば皆も来るんじゃないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:44.58,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうします
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:45.41,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:46.62,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:50.18,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君のおかげで　すっばらしい夏休みが送れそうだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:55.63,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やっぱり持つべきものは春ちゃんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:58.97,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おかげで幸先のよい夏休みがスタート
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.98,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あいつ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:09.91,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こんな大きなしかないなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:12.10,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.04,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持ってやろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:17.06,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いいわよ　ほっといて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:19.24,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お前な
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:22.74,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人の親切っていうのは素直に受けておいた方が
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:28.62,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんか羊みたいだな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:32.29,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来た来た
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.00,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭りのお誘いか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:37.20,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,えっとー　皆さんの都合はいかがですか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:38.32,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返事ください
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:40.91,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行くに決まってるんじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.12,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,な　お前は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:46.96,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,な　おい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:49.93,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春ちゃんからお祭りに誘われた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.58,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな夏の始まり
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:56.90,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おー　日本のお祭り
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:59.10,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんで浴衣姿なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:02.64,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭りと言ったら浴衣でしょう　いきじゃないすか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:05.22,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭りと言ったら雛でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:06.92,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買っちゃダメだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:08.92,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,マンション動物禁止だから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:12.44,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　より取り見取りですね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:13.90,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:15.85,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,より取り見取りすぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:18.41,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこから行くかも迷っちゃうぐらい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:21.58,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ですよね　迷っちゃいますよね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:24.65,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんかおなかすいた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:27.65,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうだな　適当に食うか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:29.14,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適当だと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.05,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ダメだ　適当は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:33.77,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺たち学生は予算が限られている
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:38.02,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高騰する屋台の食べ物を慎重かつ適格チョイスしないと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:39.95,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必ず後悔することになる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:42.37,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でもいろいろありすぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:44.08,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何を選んでいいのやら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.13,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ち着け
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.59,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こういう時はまずは定番から
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:48.59,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初戦は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.67,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たこ焼きじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:52.75,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こらこら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:58.38,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆で１個ずついろんなものを買って回し食いした方がいいんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:07:59.67,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:01.31,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さすが悠太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:02.96,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭り高校生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:06.33,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そこまで称賛する作戦か
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:09.91,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おいしい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:12.57,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当ナイスーアイディアでしたね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:15.04,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう　でも
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:17.67,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐希　いい加減　回せよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:20.86,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心配しなくても機会は均等に回ってくるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:21.93,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いずれ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:26.10,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買うたび争いが勃発してるけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.29,0:08:29.12,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あんたいつまで食べてんのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.57,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心しろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:33.24,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太らないように 俺が食ってやるよ　メリー
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.41,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あ メリー
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:41.24,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう　なんか髪の毛が羊っぽくぶわぶわってしてるからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:42.77,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:44.30,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉咲ちゃんが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.60,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんなことない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.24,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いてー
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:49.97,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:52.36,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉咲ちゃんどこ行くんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:54.84,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ　いやー
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:00.66,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あー　可愛い
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:01.94,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:05.16,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小さい頃ほしくて　よくやったんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:07.38,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なかなかうまく取れなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:10.69,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すばしっこいんですよね　金魚って
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:13.34,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はい　春ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.71,0:09:16.05,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ありがとう　茉咲ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.46,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,よし
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:20.87,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はい　嬢ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:22.04,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎重にな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.70,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑戦するのか　メリー
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:28.00,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:30.59,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待って
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.62,0:09:36.81,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嬢ちゃん　尻が青いじゃねえのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:40.22,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破れるっつの　そりゃ破れるっつの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:41.73,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はい　残念賞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:46.63,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,メリー
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.63,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うまくいくと思ったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:55.32,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おい　メリー
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.97,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まあまあ　そんなしょげるなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.93,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,メリーにしては惜しかったって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:01.37,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,触らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:02.02,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:03.96,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大体メリーって何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:06.35,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝手に変な宛名つけないでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:07.92,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やめろう　やめろうって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:09.14,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう　ほっといて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:14.29,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ちぇー　慰めにきちゃったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:17.82,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ったく可愛くねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:21.88,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉咲ちゃん大丈夫ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:23.69,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう手が尽きられません
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:25.54,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉咲ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:27.60,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やめときなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:28.52,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近付くと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:30.52,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほっとっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:34.07,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はい　どうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.09,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:38.41,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残念賞ということで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:44.91,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事にする
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:47.32,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事にするね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:51.42,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんだあれ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:56.16,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺にときはきーって怒っといて　春ちゃんにはあれですか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:59.51,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はいはい悪かったですよ　慰めが今一で
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:00.40,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あのな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:03.81,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あいつはもともと春以外は笑わねえだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:05.37,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.71,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ああ そうだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:10.90,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それじゃまるで春ちゃんに恋…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:13.59,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:15.92,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:18.86,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ええ そうなの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:22.25,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水面下でそんな恋のメロディーがあったなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.19,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水面下というより
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:27.01,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水上に出まくりバレバレなんだけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:28.51,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうなのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.42,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それであいつ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:37.39,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛くねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:44.15,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうしたどうした
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:46.62,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄ちゃんたちも青尻か
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:47.88,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:49.31,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しょうがないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:54.25,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命あるものを扱うには薄っぺらいもん　この紙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:58.58,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まあ　そこを逆にゲームとして使ってやれって狙いだろうし
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:02.35,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命を軽視しすぎる気もするけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:05.22,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,シ　価値観人それぞれだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:10.58,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こんな生き物を弄ぶような商売
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:14.38,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:28.05,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,や　気前のいいおじさんだったね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:31.04,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紙５重ねにしてくれるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:33.83,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金魚取りすぎて返しちゃったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:37.66,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大方　お前らがそうするように仕向けたんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:40.89,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しかしどうして春ちゃんなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:44.44,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この中じゃ一番男っぽくないっていうか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:47.01,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格好いいというより可愛いというか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:51.02,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,むしろ顔だけでいったら俺の好み
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:53.67,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いえいえいえ　そういう話じゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.52,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何ぶつぶつ言ってんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:56.66,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:13:00.25,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由なんか本人にだって分からねえもんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:03.87,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好きとか　嫌いなんっつの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:06.58,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:07.91,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉咲ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.91,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほれほれ　群れ中羊っぽくね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:13.35,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あー　確かに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:15.26,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,じゃなくて　助けてあげなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:17.15,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.30,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日紗子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:20.46,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来てたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:21.43,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:22.97,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お姉ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.63,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お姉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:27.18,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要君　来てたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:28.17,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:32.78,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食べる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:35.38,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お姉さま
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:38.83,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕要君の友達の千鶴って言います
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:42.42,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうです　この後花火でもやりませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:44.97,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素敵な夜をお約束しますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:46.14,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:48.01,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつそんな計画立てたの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.50,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ないよ　花火なんか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:51.99,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,チチチチチチ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:56.80,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋が計画通り進む白物なら誰も胸を痛んだりしないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:00.45,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,スーパーにならあるんじゃないですかね　花火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:03.88,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確か近くにあるんで　僕ちょっと行ってきます
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:06.47,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,じゃ　あたしたちも行こうか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:07.71,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:08.87,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でも
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:10.09,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いいのいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:13.88,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そろそろ涼しいところ行きたいなって話してたところだから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:17.02,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうですか　じゃあ　お願いします
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.74,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春ちゃんは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:21.00,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花火買いに行ったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:21.97,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人で
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:26.27,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大丈夫　焦っちゃダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:29.94,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こっちには春ちゃんからもらったキーホルダーが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:33.79,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:35.30,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉咲ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.69,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉咲ちゃんも来ますか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:41.42,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私いいや
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:42.74,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうですか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:54.15,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確かこの辺のはずなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:57.94,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:14:59.77,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:04.79,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大丈夫　焦らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:08.13,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう一回あっちの方から
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:11.56,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何してんの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:14.38,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ちょろちょろどっか行くなよ　メリー
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:19.29,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あ　落し物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:20.77,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,えっ　まじか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:21.68,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほっといて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:23.54,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何強がってんのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:26.15,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しょうがねえな　俺たちも探して
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:27.69,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いいから　余計なことしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:32.14,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あのな　お前可愛くないのは胸だけにする
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:37.75,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ったく　行こうぜ　祐希
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:38.82,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もうしゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:41.04,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人で探せるんなら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:44.08,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あんまり周りにべそ顔見せないようにね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.83,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言ったそばから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:56.50,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,メリー
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.17,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何それ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:03.81,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,で　一緒に探せってか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:06.62,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まあいいけど　それより
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:09.41,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんで千鶴ぼろぼろなの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:11.25,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こいつに聞け
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:14.28,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,７００円もしたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:19.30,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でも　ここから本殿までの間とはいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.38,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この人通りだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:22.98,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結構手間だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:25.39,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆でばらけて探しますか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:30.68,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生　クラス一丸となろうとしてるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:33.99,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠太君が真面目に参加してくれません
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:38.29,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠太君　女子の体育が気になるのも分かるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:39.75,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やる時はやる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:40.62,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お前もな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:43.20,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生　見つけました
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.42,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:49.98,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,マジですか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:53.72,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おい　ちびこ　本当にあれでやってるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:57.58,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんだ　お嬢ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:16:59.12,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,間違いない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:03.43,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あのう　その熊さん私が落としたものなんです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:04.67,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返してくれますか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:07.52,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:10.43,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これはな　おじさんが拾ったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:13.15,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから　その落とし主がこいつで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:13.84,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,証拠は
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:15.04,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.76,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,証拠まねんならやらねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:20.09,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いやいや　ですから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:22.36,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほしけりゃ　撃ち落としはいいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:24.87,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一回３００円な
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:29.05,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺絶対こんな大人にならない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:32.71,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,っつか　こんな人間にはならねえっだな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:36.43,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拾ったものを景品にする時点でアウトだね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:41.21,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毎度あ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:46.22,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ど　大バカ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:48.29,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お前いっとけの感情で
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:48.96,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放して
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:50.31,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ち着けますって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:51.57,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:54.62,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情的になると命中率が補注
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.39,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お前らは落ち着きすぎだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:58.34,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しかたねえな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.39,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ここは俺が
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:05.05,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,よし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:13.46,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こらこら　全力で頑張った人を笑っちゃダメだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:16.83,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要は全力でやってこれなんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:18.82,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほろになってねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:21.48,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頑張れ　悠太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:26.54,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これは確かに的が小さい分　難しいかも
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:29.96,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうだよ　むずかしいんだよ　な　な
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:36.18,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こういう時は　やっぱり数々なミッションを突破してきた彼でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:38.60,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:41.21,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的も大きさは問題じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:43.42,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やられる前にやる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:44.87,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それだけの話さ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:46.89,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな重い話じゃねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:54.20,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何狙ってんだ　こら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:57.28,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸せは一つに絞りませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.44,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まったく祐希は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:02.40,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しかも　今ので玉なくなっちゃったんじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:03.75,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しかたねえな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:10.47,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春たち花火買ったから　戻ってくるって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.29,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春ちゃんが戻ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:16.89,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落としたってばれちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:21.91,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おやじ　玉だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.11,0:19:24.74,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お前いきなり札が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:28.05,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆で食べ物１個ずつ買ってた意味がない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:31.12,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落としたら後で返せよ　メリー
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:35.77,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ありゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:38.09,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あんま人のこと言えねえな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:39.16,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お黙り
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:51.30,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,くっそ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:54.87,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうした　兄ちゃん　あと一発だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.07,0:19:56.26,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分かってますかな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:19:57.17,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代わろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:58.46,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お前はいい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:00.29,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,くっそ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:05.06,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰だよ　下手な鉄砲数うちゃ当たるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:07.91,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これじゃ金の飛ぶ流し
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:16.92,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南無 南無 南無　南無 南無
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:20.38,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほれ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:26.63,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,っつっかさ　年頃の娘が南無南無って祈り方はどうなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:31.26,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まあ　でもそのおかげで当たったのかもしれねえし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:33.31,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いいか　な
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:40.36,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:47.62,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春たち帰ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:49.71,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ただ今
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:50.97,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お帰りなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:55.32,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんだよ　取ってやったのは俺だっつの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:01.82,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛くねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:03.64,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後で皆でやりましょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:04.07,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:07.15,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,線香花火はやっぱり最後ですかね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:15.96,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺に近寄ると火傷するぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:17.78,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お前が近寄ってんだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.94,0:21:19.90,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴君　危ないですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:24.49,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花火がほんの少し夜を弾くと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:28.11,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そこにいつもの笑顔があって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:33.80,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花火の輝きってのは明けないもんね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:36.73,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お前の人生のように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.91,0:21:39.96,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう　ふざけてると火傷しますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:42.80,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まったく　ふざけるなんてとんでもない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:45.40,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花火持ったら　真剣勝負ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:47.78,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違うでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.29,0:21:51.95,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当たり前のように手のひらに上で増えていく日々を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:55.41,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつまでも大切に握りしめては
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:58.45,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時々そっと開いてみる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.28,0:22:00.91,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな時が来るなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:04.58,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はい　こっち見て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:06.49,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春ちゃんとツーショット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:08.05,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はい　取ります
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.97,0:22:18.53,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楽しそうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:20.25,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お姉さんもそうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:22.84,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠慮しないで　楽しんでいってください
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.05,0:22:27.97,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そういうことじゃないんだけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.36,0:22:42.73,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それに気づくのは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:45.96,JPSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと大人になってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.22,0:00:02.07,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:05.50,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无迷惘地持续闪耀的太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:07.24,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:10.15,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛若吞噬苍穹的云翳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:11.44,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:14.46,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以自由自在地睡懒觉的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:15.92,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:17.77,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:19.59,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:20.78,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:23.27,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:28.22,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:34.71,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.59,0:00:41.29,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:22.06,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去-玩-吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:23.32,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:24.62,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:25.68,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:29.24,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有很多人等着我去拯救呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:31.86,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救人 怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:33.86,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道祐希在做志愿者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:34.78,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:39.45,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是那种只会为钱行动的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:42.48,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…在做什么 破案吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:46.17,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐希 不快点的话大家就都死了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:48.26,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.85,0:02:54.84,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:56.38,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:02:59.32,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:01.97,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还什么都没说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:04.03,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不听也知道你要说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.82,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:06.67,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:07.38,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:08.76,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 去哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:11.49,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说我不去玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:15.18,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正做作业呢  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:16.65,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:18.55,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一分钟 一分钟就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:20.28,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我说句话 就让我说一句话啊太太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.49,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了这个的话肌肤就会绸缎般光滑啊这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:23.84,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是推销员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:27.85,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:30.31,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 千鹤君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:32.94,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真亏了你能找到我家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:34.16,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:35.37,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:39.77,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:42.01,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连小春也不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:43.98,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 也不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:46.18,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:49.24,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 要一起做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:50.67,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起做？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:53.34,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.72,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做点心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:58.09,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然以前几乎没有做过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:00.97,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过反正放假也是闲着  就想着要不要试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:02.48,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一起做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.13,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好 做吧做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:08.29,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:11.24,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 能麻烦你和下那边的面粉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:12.20,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:13.05,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:17.36,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤君挺擅长的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:22.11,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 过奖了啦 我还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:24.40,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:26.73,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.65,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能做得好吃就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:31.75,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:34.44,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春光顾自己吃 好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:37.58,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 不好意思 给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:44.06,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 又甜又软入口即化啊 真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:46.89,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待成品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:48.71,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:52.80,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 做好以后 把这个也送到大家那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:54.60,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:57.42,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:58.57,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的异空间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:01.03,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得像要失去自我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:02.02,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:04.73,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做腻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:08.36,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是都已经到这一步了 不做到最后的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:11.60,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么 新的我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:12.63,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:17.53,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想去玩才上门去找大家的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:18.75,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.94,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是难得的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:24.25,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都缩在凉爽的家里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:27.06,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天特别热嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.37,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还有一个月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:31.44,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会出去玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:33.75,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:35.39,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典之类的怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:36.38,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:37.93,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:40.03,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上的话也比较凉快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:42.54,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去邀请的话大家应该会来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:44.58,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:45.41,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:46.62,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:50.18,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福 我也许能过个美好的暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:55.63,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然小春是不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:58.97,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了他 暑假才开始有好兆头…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.98,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:09.91,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然只有这么大的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:12.10,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很重诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.04,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:17.06,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:19.24,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:22.74,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人的好意还是坦率地接受下来比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:28.62,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得像只羊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:32.29,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.00,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典的邀请吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:37.20,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 大家都有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:38.32,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回复我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:40.91,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定要去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.12,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:46.96,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:49.93,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春邀请我去祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.58,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天就这样开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:56.90,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 日本的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:59.10,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥要穿浴衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:02.64,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到祭典不就是浴衣吗 不是当然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:05.22,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到祭典的话是小鸡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:06.92,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准买哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:08.92,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为公寓禁止养宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:12.44,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是琳琅满目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:13.90,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:15.85,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都看花眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:18.41,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道从哪边开始逛才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:21.58,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 好纠结
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:24.65,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:27.65,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 随便吃点东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:29.14,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说随便？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.05,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准随便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:33.77,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学生的预算是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:38.02,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不慎重地选择街边摊的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:39.95,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:42.37,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是东西太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:44.08,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选什么才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.13,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.59,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候首先要从必选项目开始啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:48.59,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.67,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章鱼烧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:52.75,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:58.38,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人买一种然后换着吃不是更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:07:59.67,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:01.31,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是犹太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:02.96,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:06.33,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个战术也不至于被称赞到那种地步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:09.91,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:12.57,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好主意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:15.04,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 不过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:17.67,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐希 你悠着点 换我吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:20.86,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 机会是平等的 会轮到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:21.93,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:26.10,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次买都会爆发战争啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.29,0:08:29.12,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要吃到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.57,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:33.24,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了避免你长胖 我会帮你吃的 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.41,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:41.24,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 因为头发像羊毛一样蓬松
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:42.77,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:44.30,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉咲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.60,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.24,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:49.97,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:52.36,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉咲 你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:54.84,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:00.66,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:01.94,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:05.16,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候因为想要经常玩这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:07.38,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过很难捞到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:10.69,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金鱼挺灵活的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:13.34,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.71,0:09:16.05,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 茉咲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.46,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:20.87,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:22.04,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.70,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要挑战吗 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:28.00,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:30.59,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.62,0:09:36.81,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 你还太嫩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:40.22,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 这个破了 连网都破了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:41.73,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 鼓励奖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:46.63,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.63,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想着会很顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:55.32,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.97,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算啦 别这么沮丧嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.93,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差那么一点点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:01.37,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:02.02,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:03.96,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底玛丽是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:06.35,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擅自给我起奇怪的绰号啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:07.92,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:09.14,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:14.29,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切　亏我还来安慰你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:17.82,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一点都不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:21.88,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉咲没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:23.69,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不用管她了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:25.54,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉咲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:27.60,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说别这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:28.52,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠近的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:30.52,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:34.07,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.09,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:38.41,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为鼓励奖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:44.91,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:47.32,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会好好珍惜的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:51.42,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:56.16,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我就呲牙发火 对小春就那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:59.51,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 真不好意思啊 我不擅长安慰人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:00.40,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:03.81,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙本来就不会对春以外的人笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:05.37,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.71,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:10.90,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就像喜欢上小春…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:13.59,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:15.92,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:18.86,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶诶 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:22.25,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道还有这种恋爱旋律潜藏在水下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.19,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是藏在水下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:27.01,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说已经完全浮上水面一目了然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:28.51,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.42,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那家伙才…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:37.39,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:44.15,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:46.62,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥你们也很嫩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:47.88,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:49.31,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:54.25,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要捞取活物的话这纸也太薄了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:58.58,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过反过来说 这就是游戏的可玩之处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:02.35,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然会有草菅性命的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:05.22,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘 价值观是因人而异的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:10.58,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样玩弄活物的生意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:14.38,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:28.05,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 真是个慷慨的大叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:31.04,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然帮我们糊了5层纸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:33.83,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果因为金鱼捞得太多 还还给他几条
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:37.66,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计是你俩诱拐他那么做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:40.89,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来为什么是小春？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:44.44,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是我们几个里面最不像男人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:47.01,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是帅不如说是可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:51.02,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只说脸的话倒刚好是我喜欢的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:53.67,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不 我不是想说这个来着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.52,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你唧唧歪歪什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:56.66,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:13:00.25,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说理由 可能她自己也不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:03.87,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么喜欢 什么讨厌的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:06.58,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:07.91,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉咲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.91,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啦 很像羊群里面的一只羊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:13.35,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:15.26,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对吧 快去帮她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:17.15,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.30,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日纱子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:20.46,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:21.43,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:22.97,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.63,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:27.18,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要君 你来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:28.17,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:32.78,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:35.38,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:38.83,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是要君的朋友 叫千鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:42.42,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 稍后要不要去放烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:44.97,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证这会是个美好的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:46.14,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:48.01,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候定了这种计划啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.50,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有什么烟花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:51.99,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切切切切切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:56.80,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果连恋爱都按计划进行的话 谁都不会被打动的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:00.45,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超市会不会有啊 烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:03.88,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得附近就有 我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:06.47,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:07.71,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:08.87,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:10.09,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:13.88,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正说要去凉快点的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:17.02,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.74,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:21.00,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去买烟花了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:21.97,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:26.27,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧 不能急
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:29.94,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这儿还有小春给的钥匙链…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:33.79,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:35.30,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉咲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.69,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉咲也一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:41.42,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:42.74,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:54.15,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该在这附近的才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:57.94,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:14:59.77,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:04.79,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 不要着急
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:08.13,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再从那边开始找一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:11.56,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:14.38,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要到处乱跑啊 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:19.29,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是丢了东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:20.77,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:21.68,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:23.54,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在逞什么强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:26.15,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法 我们也来找…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:27.69,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了啦 别多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:32.14,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 我还以为你不可爱的只有胸部…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:37.75,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 走吧 祐希
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:38.82,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管她了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:41.04,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你一个人也能找得到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:44.08,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就别对周围的人摆出一副要哭的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.83,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才刚说完
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:56.50,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.17,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:03.81,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 就是让我们一起找咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:06.62,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以倒是可以 不过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:09.41,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么千鹤鼻青脸肿的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:11.25,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:14.28,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还花了700日元呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:19.30,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 虽然说是在从这里到大殿的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.38,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这人来人往的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:22.98,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得费点力气了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:25.39,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家分头找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:30.68,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 班上同学都在想着要齐心协力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:33.99,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠太同学却不认真参与
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:38.29,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠太同学 我知道你很想去看女生上体育课
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:39.75,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但该认真的时候还是要认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:40.62,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:43.20,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.42,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:49.98,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:53.72,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小不点 真的是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:57.58,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:16:59.12,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:03.43,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那只熊是我不小心掉了的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:04.67,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能还给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:07.52,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:10.43,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊 是大叔我捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:13.15,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说啊 弄丢它的就是这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:13.84,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:15.04,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.76,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有证据的话不能给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:20.09,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是 所以说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:22.36,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的话 射中它就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:24.87,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次300日元
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:29.05,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不要变成这种大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:32.71,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说 绝对不要变成这种人类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:36.43,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他把捡来的东西拿来当奖品的时候就已经不是人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:41.21,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:46.22,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:48.29,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太冲动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:48.96,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:50.31,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:51.57,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:54.62,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情用事的话命中率会降低
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.39,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩也太冷静了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:58.34,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.39,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就由我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:05.05,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:13.46,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不能嘲笑全力以赴的人哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:16.83,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要可是竭尽全力才做到这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:18.82,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不是帮我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:21.48,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 悠太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:26.54,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个确实…靶子太小了 很难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:29.96,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 很难的 是吧 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:36.18,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候 果然就需要过关斩将的这位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:38.60,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:41.21,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靶子的大小不是问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:43.42,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被杀之前杀死对方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:44.87,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:46.89,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是那么严重的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:54.20,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都在瞄准什么啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:57.28,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福是无法集中在一个物体上的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.44,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐希真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:02.40,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他刚才把子弹都打光了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:03.75,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:10.47,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春说他们买好烟花回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.29,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:16.89,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄丢钥匙链的事情要被他知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:21.91,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 给我子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.11,0:19:24.74,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接用纸币啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:28.05,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家每个人买一种吃的就没意义了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:31.12,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我射中的话待会要还我钱哦 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:35.77,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:38.09,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没什么资格说别人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:39.16,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:51.30,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:54.87,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样啊小哥 只剩一颗子弹了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.07,0:19:56.26,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:19:57.17,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要换人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:58.46,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:00.29,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:05.06,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁说万发总有一发中的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:07.91,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子钱就打水漂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:16.92,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南无 南无 南无 南无 南无
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:20.38,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:26.63,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 年轻的女孩子在怎么能南无南无地祈祷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:31.26,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 不过我没准就是多亏了那个才能射中的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:33.31,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:40.36,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:47.62,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春他们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:49.71,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:50.97,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:55.32,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 是我帮你取回来的诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:01.82,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:03.64,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会大家一起放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:04.07,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:07.15,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙女棒果然还是要留到最后的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:15.96,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近我的话 可是会被烧伤的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:17.78,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你靠过来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.94,0:21:19.90,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤君 很危险的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:24.49,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当烟花在夜空中纷散的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:28.11,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会出现一如既往的笑颜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:33.80,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花的璀璨真是转瞬即逝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:36.73,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你的人生一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.91,0:21:39.96,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再胡闹的话会烧伤的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:42.80,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 胡闹什么的真是不像话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:45.40,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然手握烟花 就要认真一决胜负才是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:47.78,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.29,0:21:51.95,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像理所当然地 在手心中渐渐增加的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:55.41,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时都珍惜地握在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:58.45,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时也会悄悄打开来看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.28,0:22:00.91,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到那样的时刻竟然会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:04.58,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 看镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:06.49,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小春单独合影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:08.05,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我要拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.97,0:22:18.53,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:20.25,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:22.84,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气 一起来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.05,0:22:27.97,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.36,0:22:42.73,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以察觉到那一刻的来临
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:45.96,cnsub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因为我们长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:23:01.43,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕は泣き虫で　悔しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:08.50,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だけどあなたに今伝えたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.66,0:23:13.99,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ただまっすぐに僕を見つめる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.15,0:23:22.42,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強くて優しいその瞳に応えるために
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:27.91,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつしか見失ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:34.17,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一番大切なものも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.33,0:23:39.63,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっとあなたが教えてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.80,0:23:47.52,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たしかにそう思えるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.00,0:23:55.27,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕は弱虫で　嫌だった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.46,0:24:02.18,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だけどもっともっと強くなるから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.36,0:24:10.91,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたのことを守れるような僕になるから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.09,0:24:17.22,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから　少し待ってて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:23:01.43,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不甘心只当个爱哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:08.50,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把这种心情传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.66,0:23:13.99,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要移开目光注视着我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.15,0:23:22.42,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我可以回应你坚强而温柔的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:27.91,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉就丢失了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:34.17,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最珍惜的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.33,0:23:39.63,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而你教我如何找回它
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.80,0:23:47.52,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发自肺腑地这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.00,0:23:55.27,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好讨厌我的懦弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.46,0:24:02.18,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想要变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.36,0:24:10.91,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为能够守护你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.09,0:24:17.22,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请稍稍等我一下吧
